A new everyday necklace- it's got a little grit and a little sparkle. It's  simple and modern. The pyrite stone has a beautiful texture, and a rustic, simple shape. Smoky glass beads trail up the gunmetal chain neckline and frame the lobster clasp. It's designed to rest just under the hollow of your throat, making it perfect for layering and very comfortable. Your necklace will arrive wrapped and ready for gift giving.

The Specs: 
Pyrite stone 
Glass beads 
Gunmetal brass chain 
Measure 16"/40cm long

name: Love Buckle
description: A little letterpress love. This buckle uses letters from a mismatched letterpress collection. A sweet buckle for your sweetie. This buckle measures 2 1/2" by 3 1/4" and will fit either a 1 1/2" or 1 3/4" snap belt. It is cast from pewter and sealed with a protective resin coating, so it's incredibly durable. Your new buckle will arrive wrapped and ready for gift giving.

name: Drop Necklace. Choose your finish.
description: This necklace is streamlined, framed and gorgeous. A simple hand formed metal teardrop frames a faceted blue, apatite stone. The metal has a lovely texture, a simple shape and soft patina, leaving the stone to steal the show. Necklace is 18" and available finishes are natural brass, raw copper or sterling silver, perfect for layering and easy to wear. Your necklace will arrive wrapped and ready for gift giving.

name: Weekend Earrings
description:

They've been given a brushed finish and tumbled for strength and shine. Available finishes are natural brass, raw copper, sterling silver and 14k gold fill. Your new earrings will arrive wrapped and ready for gift giving.

The Specs:
Czech glass
Natural Brass
Raw Copper
Sterling silver
14k Gold Fill
